  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to find out if data can be provided by external sensor technology
      which is suitable for controlling the therapy of patients with cardiac recompensation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
  <start_date>October 2011</start_date>
